{"tid":837418,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德三大車廠(奧迪、Benz及寶馬)在華測試無人車","createTime":"2018-09-26T11:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T11:05:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d418d8c35da55502e72a672be9537d10688f3c4f","tid":837418,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:00:36.000Z","msg":"英國《金融時報》報道，德國三大汽車製造商奧迪、平治(Benz，又稱奔馳)及寶馬，已經同意與中國地圖和數據供應商合作，在中國測試自動駕駛汽車。<br />\n<br />\n奧迪本月在無錫啟動了為期四日的自動駕駛測試，並將於明年初在無錫建立一個研發和測試中心，計劃招聘150名員工。該公司還將與華為和中國移動(00941)合作開發遠程訊息技術。<br />\n<br />\n今年7月，平治母公司戴姆勒(Daimler)表示，其測試車輛將在北京開始道路測試，並正開發自己的內部系統。<br />\n<br />\n寶馬則於今年5月，獲得了在上海測試自動駕駛汽車的牌照，為首家在中國獲得此類牌照的家外國公司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1953234/%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%A0%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1953234%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%258F%25AF%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25A9%25A6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BB%258A&d=Df%2F4XjLza5srvzb%2B%2BQj%2Fb6MP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=bfbef9b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1953234/%E5%BE%B7%E4%B8%89%E5%A4%A7%E8%BB%8A%E5%BB%A0%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E6%B8%AC%E8%A9%A6%E7%84%A1%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A</a>"},{"pid":"fc9e15ff9384a2cae90d922fa913c67da6630bb8","tid":837418,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T11:05:33.000Z","msg":"所有技術資料已經複製好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}